## Verification Checklist

Before considering a React component complete:

- [ ] Component under 300 lines (or split if multiple responsibilities)
- [ ] Custom hooks extracted only when reused 2+ times
- [ ] State kept local unless shared by 2+ siblings
- [ ] No derived state in `useEffect`
- [ ] Boolean props use `is`/`has`/`can`/`should` prefix
- [ ] Props count ≤ 10 (or grouped into objects)
- [ ] No `useMemo`/`useCallback` without measured need
- [ ] Maximum 1 level of ternary nesting
- [ ] All list items have stable, unique keys (no index)
- [ ] All props explicitly typed
